front.title: Point Man (V)
front.gametext: USED: Move a trooper as a 'react' to a battle where you have a leader. OR During any draw phase, place a card from hand under your Used Pile to take any one card into hand from Force Pile; reshuffle.  LOST: During a battle at a site, cancel Keep Your Eyes Open.
front.lore: In a military situation, on a regional or galactic scale, commands sometimes get misinterpreted. A local commander giving orders is far more reliable.
